en la trampa del señor Zheng.

00:08:24.354 --> 00:08:25.474
¿Trampa?

00:08:25.994 --> 00:08:27.234
Yuehai está prosperando.

00:08:27.794 --> 00:08:29.513
Dada esta trayectoria,

00:08:30.354 --> 00:08:32.673
